Source: mcp-sdk
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: MCP SDK Team <support@mcp-sdk.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12),
               cmake,
               pkg-config,
               libssl-dev,
               libgtest-dev,
               libgmock-dev
# 注意：构建时使用 /usr/local/lib64/ 下的 OpenSSL 库
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/mcp-sdk/cpp-mcp-sdk
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/mcp-sdk/cpp-mcp-sdk
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/mcp-sdk/cpp-mcp-sdk.git

Package: libmcp-sdk
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libssl, libcrypto3
Description: MCP SDK - Model Context Protocol C++ SDK runtime libraries
 This package provides the MCP (Model Context Protocol) C++ SDK shared libraries
 including both client and server components. The SDK enables communication
 between AI models and external tools through a standardized protocol.
 .
 Features:
  - Client library for connecting to MCP servers
  - Server library for implementing MCP services
  - Support for multiple transport protocols (HTTP, HTTPS, IPC)
  - Comprehensive logging and error handling
  - Cross-platform compatibility
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries needed to run applications
 using the MCP SDK.

Package: libmcp-sdk-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libmcp-sdk
Description: MCP SDK - Model Context Protocol C++ SDK development files
 This package provides the MCP (Model Context Protocol) C++ SDK development
 files including header files and CMake configuration files needed to
 develop applications using the MCP SDK.
 .
 Features:
  - Complete header files for both client and server APIs
  - CMake configuration files for easy integration
  - Example programs and documentation
  - Cross-platform compatibility
 .
 This package contains the development files needed to build applications
 using the MCP SDK.

Package: mcp-sdk-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libmcp-sdk
Description: MCP SDK - Model Context Protocol C++ SDK tools and examples
 This package provides example programs and tools for the MCP (Model Context Protocol)
 C++ SDK. These tools demonstrate how to use the SDK for both client and server
 implementations.
 .
 Features:
  - Example client programs for HTTP, HTTPS, and IPC protocols
  - Example server implementations
  - Filesystem server example
  - Test programs and utilities
 .
 This package contains the example programs and tools for the MCP SDK.
